                translation: "My words are easy to understand and easy to put into practice, yet almost no one in the world manages to understand or practice them. My words have a source; my actions have a guiding principle. It's simply that people don't recognize this, and so they don't recognize me. Those who understand me are rare, which is exactly what makes me valuable. That is why the sage dresses in coarse cloth while carrying jade close to their heart.",
                theme: "treasures",
